# Normalize all text to LF everywhere — committed artifacts (e.g. the OpenAPI
# contract) are byte-compared against generated output in CI, and Prettier +
# .editorconfig already mandate LF. Without this, Windows checkouts get CRLF
# and the contract gate false-positives (caught by the Windows CI leg).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binaries
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
